程序包 gameSettings

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Debug
    A singleton class that record if the debug mode is open.
    DebugTest  
    Dialog
    Take some String as input and pop up a window to show this messages.
    GameComplete
    A singleton class that record if the game is complete.
    GameCompleteTest  
    GameLogger
    Class GameLogger is used to record game logs.
    GameRecord
    The class is used when a level is complete, the game is complete or Save Score function is used.
    Music
    Control background music for the game.
